Name: Average resolution time following 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Difference in average time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' vs. 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + In Call' to understand its impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' before moving to any next activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Maximum time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' before achieving resolution
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Closed' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Time until 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' from case start
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Distribution of time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' across different organization countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Average delay introduced by 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in case resolution compared to cases without this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer does not occur

Name: Total time cases spend in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' when followed by 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average time to resolve a case after 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' compared to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Cycle time of cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in comparison to cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case
